<p>I have the following in the data-config file. The database returns 2k rows. and when indexed in the solr admin overview page I see maxDocs as 2k rows(the numbers match) but numdocs is 24.And the <em>:</em> query returns 24 only. Not sure what's wrong. I am a beginner in Apache solr and starting to practice with small chunk of data.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;dataConfig&gt;   &lt;dataSource type="JdbcDataSource"             driver="com.mysql.jdbc.Driver"             url="jdbc:mysql://host:port/schema_name"             batchSize="-1"             user="username"             password="password" /&gt;    &lt;document name="product"&gt;     &lt;entity name="store" rootEntity="True" query="select mid,name,display_name,address,email,pincode,b.latitude,b.longitude,city,locality,b.lid,b.locid,i.item_id,pos_code,i.bid,i.cid,short_description,description,CONCAT_WS(field_1,',',field_2,',',field_3,',',field_4,',',field_5,',',field_6) as item_feature,br.bname,c.cname,sku_count,unit_price,final_price    from business b join locality loc on b.locid = loc.locid join location l on l.lid = loc.lid join item_test i on i.store_id=b.mid join brand br on i.bid=br.bid join category c on c.cid = i.cid  where b.status='A' and i.status='A' and sku_count &gt;0 and  b.isItemStore ='Y' "&gt;         &lt;field column="mid" name="id"/&gt;         &lt;field column="lid" name="lid"/&gt;         &lt;field column="locid" name="locid"/&gt;         &lt;field column="name" name="name"/&gt;         &lt;field column="display_name" name="display_name"/&gt;         &lt;field column="address" name="address"/&gt;         &lt;field column="email" name="email"/&gt;         &lt;field column="pincode" name="pincode"/&gt;         &lt;field column="latitude" name="latitude"/&gt;         &lt;field column="longitude" name="longitude"/&gt;         &lt;field column="city" name="city"/&gt;         &lt;field column="locality" name="locality"/&gt;         &lt;field column="item_id" name="item_id"/&gt;             &lt;field column="pos_code" name="pos_code" /&gt;         &lt;field column="bid" name="bid"/&gt;         &lt;field column="cid" name="cid"/&gt;             &lt;field column="short_description" name="short_description"/&gt;         &lt;field column="description" name="item_desc"/&gt;         &lt;field column="item_feature" name="item_feature"/&gt;                      &lt;field column="bname" name="brand_name" /&gt;         &lt;field column="cname" name="category_name" /&gt;                             &lt;field column="sku_count" name="sku_count" /&gt;             &lt;field column="unit_price" name="unit_price" /&gt;           &lt;field column="final_price" name="final_price" /&gt;        &lt;/entity&gt;     &lt;/document&gt; &lt;/dataConfig&gt; </code></pre>